Iteration 1/3
Description: Fix and implement WCAG 2.2 Level AA accessibility patterns in React, shadcn/ui, and TanStack Start projects. Use when fixing accessibility issues, implementing accessible components, adding ARIA attributes, fixing keyboard navigation, improving focus management, fixing color contrast, fixing contrast ratio, adding alt text, making forms accessible, adding skip links, making a modal accessible, fixing tab order, adding ARIA attributes, building an accessible dropdown menu, or writing accessible React code. Also use when users mention "make this accessible", "fix a11y", "add aria", "keyboard support", "screen reader support", "focus trap", "accessible dialog/modal/menu/form", or "tab order broken".
